SD-Tris
-----------------------------------------------------------

Authors
-----------------------------------------------------------
	o David Demelier <markand@malikania.fr>
		Main developer

Prerequisites
-----------------------------------------------------------

SD-Tris requires all of these libraries to be installed:
	o SDL		(http://www.libsdl.org/)
	o SDL_image	(http://www.libsdl.org/projects/SDL_image/)
	o SDL_ttf	(http://www.libsdl.org/projects/SDL_ttf/)
	o wing		(http://hg.malikania.fr/wing)

SD-Tris also needs these tools:
	o cmake		(http://cmake.org/)

Compile from Unix
-----------------------------------------------------------

Compiling:
	$ mkdir _build_
	$ cd _build_
	$ cmake .. -DPREFIX=/usr/local
	$ make
	# make install
